collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (10 total Queries, 10 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT `a`.`id` as `id`, `a`.`tgl` as `tgl`, `a`.`total` as `total`, `a`.`subtotal` as `subtotal`, `a`.`ppn` as `ppn`, `a`.`discount` as `discount`, `a`.`laba` as `laba`, `a`.`pelanggan` as `pelanggan`, `a`.`buktibayar` as `buktibayar`, `b`.`nama` as `nama_pelanggan`, `b`.`nohp` as `nohp`, `c`.`icon` as `icon`, `c`.`nama_tipe` as `nama_tipe` FROM `penjualan` as `a` LEFT JOIN `pelanggan` as `b` ON `a`.`id_pelanggan` = `b`.`id` JOIN `tipe_bayar` as `c` ON `c`.`id` = `id_tipe_bayar` WHERE `a`.`id_toko` = '1' AND `a`.`delete` <> 1 ORDER BY `a`.`id` DESC LIMIT 10
